data.description: This amazing Crestmont II Plan home by Pulte is built of white limestone. Nestled in tall oaks on a quiet cul-de-sac, this home is in Grandview Hills a lovely subdivision with great schools! Open Floor plan offers master suite and office/5th bedroom on main floor. Gourmet kitchen with gas cooktop, corian counters has center island and sunny breakfast nook with window seating and opens to spacious family room with Fireplace and which has a wall of windows overlooking view of an oasis garden with pool and spa. Spa style Master Bath has double vanities, separate shower and large soaking tub. New wood laminate flooring in DR with chair rail encourages conversations. Designer colors throughout. Rich travertine tile flooring adds elegance. Upstairs offers spacious additional 3 bedrooms,  a Jack and Jill bath and 3rd full bath as well as a second living area. Minutes to shopping, restaurants and Lakeline Mall.
